What you need to know:

Gor Mahia fans were eagerly waiting to watch the Brazilian play against AFC Leopards in the derby on Sunday, and might have to wait a little longer for his debut.They are also waiting to see if he will raise the bar on the club's blunt attack which has been misfiring in league matches, including Sunday’s barren draw against Leopards. Because the world believes that the best footballers come from Brazil, just as people trust every Kenyan to be a prolific distance runner!